title: COAST ORB / reeds with buoy
description: Visual Calculus notes that this is a good place to hide things.

dialogueTree.title: Inland Empire: "That patch of reeds over there -- i..."
dialogueTree.english: That patch of reeds over there -- it's a great place to hide something. Kind of out of the way, being so close to the water.
dialogueTree.polish: Ta kępa trzcin o tam – świetne miejsce, żeby coś ukryć. Trochę na uboczu, bardzo blisko wody.
dialogueTree.belarusian: Та купа чароту там – выдатнае месца, каб нешта схаваць. Трохі ў баку, вельмі блізка да вады.

links.title: You: "Wait, I can't see anything interest..."
links.english: Wait, I can't see anything interesting...
links.belarusian: Хвіліна. Я не бачу нічога цікавага...

links.title: Inland Empire: "You don't have a reason to -- yet."
links.english: You don't have a reason to -- yet.
links.polish: Nie masz ku temu powodu. Jeszcze.
links.belarusian: У цябе няма на тое падставы. Пакуль.

links.title: Inland Empire: "Nothing. Just a hunch. The hunch pa..."
links.english: Nothing. Just a hunch. The hunch passes, leaving you there, by the old buoy bobbing in the water. Time to go.
links.polish: O nic. To tylko przeczucie. Które po chwili mija, zostawiając cię osamotnionego tam, przy starej, kołyszącej się na wodzie boi. Czas ruszać.
links.belarusian: О нічога. Гэта толькі прадчуванне. Якое праз момант мінае, пакідаючы цябе самотным там, каля старой, калыхаючайся на вадзе буі. Час рушыць.
